<div class="container-fluid w-50 mt-5 mb-5">
  <p>
    Please note that this application is intended for self-training purposes. It is not a functioning e-commerce platform, and no actual purchases will take place. The "BUY" button is provided for demonstration purposes only. You are not required to provide any personal or payment information.
  </p>
  <p>
    When the user clicks the "BUY" button, the application will simulate the process of completing a transaction. However, since this is a practice app, no actual purchases are being made.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid d-flex flex-column w-50">
  <h2>Checkout</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-9">Item</div>
    <div class="col-1 text-center">Qty</div>
    <div class="col-2 text-end">Total Costs</div>
  </div>

  <% @cart_items.each do |item| %>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-9">
        <div><%= item.product.name %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-1 text-center">
        <div><%= item.quantity %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-2 text-end">
        $<%= item.product.price * item.quantity %>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-9">-</div>
    <div class="col-1 text-center">-</div>
    <div class="col-2 text-end"><%= @subtotal %></div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">

    <%= button_to "Checkout", user_purchases_path(@user) %>

  </div>
</div>
